				<div class="hvres-meaning small">• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Ph%E1%BA%A1m-T%C3%B4ng-M%E1%BA%A1i/B%E1%BA%AFc-s%E1%BB%A9-ng%E1%BA%ABu-th%C3%A0nh/poem-LBhM9J_jV3KiRyPr0F8Kyg">Bắc sứ ngẫu thành - 北使偶成</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ph%E1%BA%A1m-T%C3%B4ng-M%E1%BA%A1i/author-EY3eHTvDpkwLbISMoUQtYg">Phạm Tông Mại</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/Bi%E1%BB%87t-T%C3%B4-H%E1%BB%81/poem-oYz7dQSnMMqVizRDjO6LMQ">Biệt Tô Hề - 別蘇徯</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-B%E1%BA%A1ch/%C4%90%E1%BA%A1i-t%E1%BA%B7ng-vi%E1%BB%85n/poem-Fp_L9lk2pDCuDY0atWd0cw">Đại tặng viễn - 代贈遠</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-B%E1%BA%A1ch/author-8WYDeeki5xZo8eD-k6Sk5A">Lý Bạch</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/K%C3%BD-Nh%E1%BA%A1c-Ch%C3%A2u-Gi%E1%BA%A3-t%C6%B0-m%C3%A3-l%E1%BB%A5c-tr%C6%B0%E1%BB%A3ng-Ba-Ch%C3%A2u-Nghi%C3%AAm-b%C3%A1t-s%E1%BB%A9-qu%C3%A2n-l%C6%B0%E1%BB%A1ng-c%C3%A1c-l%C3%A3o-ng%C5%A9-th%E1%BA%ADp-v%E1%BA%ADn/poem-EIg64qLyc1Dqi6QQkVPfZQ">Ký Nhạc Châu Giả tư mã lục trượng, Ba Châu Nghiêm bát sứ quân lưỡng các lão ngũ thập vận - 寄岳州賈司馬六丈、巴州嚴八使君兩閣老五十韻</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nh%E1%BA%A1c-L%C3%B4i-Ph%C3%A1t/%C3%94-%C3%B4-ca/poem--nkwKog4rhovNtymFbWpRg">Ô ô ca - 烏烏歌</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nh%E1%BA%A1c-L%C3%B4i-Ph%C3%A1t/author-5J0P_EDGEC1h1gar2eA3WQ">Nhạc Lôi Phát</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%B4ng-B%E1%BA%A3n-thi%E1%BB%81n-s%C6%B0/S%C6%A1n-c%C6%B0-b%C3%A1ch-v%E1%BB%8Bnh-k%E1%BB%B3-027/poem-GNq-akVzhUXN4ZGFKyaJ7w">Sơn cư bách vịnh kỳ 027 - 山居百詠其二十七</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%B4ng-B%E1%BA%A3n-thi%E1%BB%81n-s%C6%B0/author-jnvtlp5PrNS3FoOBBGt7-w">Tông Bản thiền sư</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Phi-Khanh/T%E1%BA%A1-B%C4%83ng-H%E1%BB%93-t%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Bng-c%C3%B4ng-t%E1%BB%A9-m%C3%A3/poem-2uGnNsXgDt1YK5Jpe4qJOg">Tạ Băng Hồ tướng công tứ mã - 謝冰壼相公賜馬</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Phi-Khanh/author-3K5mDhkNpasGeB0z-64AmA">Nguyễn Phi Khanh</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-%C4%90%E1%BB%99ng/T%E1%BB%87-l%C6%B0/poem-zF5F2fuJpi-tBv6pkHM98A">Tệ lư - 斃驢</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-%C4%90%E1%BB%99ng/author-PuXksgdBieGiSiRcb1zBAQ">Lý Động</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-%C4%90%E1%BB%81/Thanh-Quy%E1%BA%BFt-giang/poem-hCqBIMPo_OjxnyKK666K8Q">Thanh Quyết giang - 清決江</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-%C4%90%E1%BB%81/author-YFWZ8afu7g2IoLevX1_E2Q">Nguyễn Đề</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Ng%E1%BB%8Dc-Quy%E1%BA%BFn/T%E1%BB%B1-%C4%91i%E1%BA%BFu/poem-ZRHP1qz4lVkqBnCiDpmN5g">Tự điếu - 自吊</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Ng%E1%BB%8Dc-Quy%E1%BA%BFn/author-O3OAo7wTsvdoZtU7gOrz_g">Lương Ngọc Quyến</a>)<br/></div>	</div>
